CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 County Boards of Education – Student Electronic Communication Device Use
3 Policy – Establishment
4 (Maryland Phone–Free Schools Act)
5 (Joanne C. Benson Maryland Phone–Free Schools Act)
6 FOR the purpose of requiring each county board of education to develop and implement,
7 not later than a certain school year, a policy limiting prohibiting the use of an
8 electronic communication device by a student during the school day except under
9 certain circumstances; and generally relating to county boards of education and a
10 student electronic communication device use policy.
11 BY adding to
12 Article – Education
